	*** Welcome to the Rings Ray Tracing Engine ***

* To run this package you will need to perform a few simple steps:

1. Make sure you have java 1.4 or higher installed.
2. Download the latest Rings jar file from j3d.sf.net and put it in
   the rings/bin directory.
3. Run "Rings/bin/rings". If you are asked what application to use to
   open this file with, select the Terminal application found in
   Applications/Utilities.

